# Business Simulation MMO - Product Overview

## What We're Building

A multiplayer business simulation game where players create and manage companies, trade assets, participate in corporate governance, and compete in a dynamic economic environment. Think "SimCity meets Wall Street" in a persistent online world.

## Core Game Experience

### Company Management
- **Create & Run Companies**: Start your own business empire from scratch
- **Shareholder System**: Issue shares, manage ownership, and handle investor relations
- **Corporate Governance**: Hold board meetings, vote on major decisions, and shape company policy
- **Financial Management**: Track profits, manage expenses, and grow your business value

### Trading & Markets
- **Asset Trading**: Buy and sell stocks, bonds, and commodities in real-time markets
- **Portfolio Management**: Build diverse investment portfolios and track performance
- **Market Dynamics**: Experience supply and demand, price fluctuations, and market volatility
- **Trading History**: Complete transaction records and performance analytics

### Work & Employment
- **Job Creation**: Post job openings and hire talented employees
- **Career Progression**: Work for other companies, build skills, and advance your career
- **Salary Management**: Negotiate compensation and manage payroll
- **Performance Tracking**: Monitor productivity and employee satisfaction

### Social & Governance
- **Real-time Chat**: Communicate with other players and company members
- **Government System**: Participate in economic policy, taxation, and regulation
- **Achievement System**: Unlock milestones and showcase your business success
- **Global Community**: Connect with players worldwide in multiple languages

